info.description:
RealLib3 is a C++ library that allows computation of real numbers exactly.
pyreallib is a Pyrex wrapper for the RealLib3 Library. It compiles on Linux (x86
and AMD64) and PowerPC (OSX 10.3 and higher).
info.name: pyreallib
info.summary: A Pyrex wrapper for the RealLib3 library
